          <p>
            <monospace>[1,] 4.024 0.091 27748 27669 1.4 0.023 3.845 4.203 400</monospace>
          </p>
        </list-item>
      </list>
      <p>In the above codes, the confidence level of the confidence intervals was set to the default 95%. The CL argument can be used to change the confidence level to 90, as below.</p>
      <list list-type="simple">
        <list-item>
          <p>
            <monospace>&gt; fert(ZWIR71,Indicator = "gfr", CL = 90)</monospace>
          </p>
        </list-item>
