          </p>
        </list-item>
      </list>
      <p>The <monospace>fert</monospace> function allows for class level rates by declaring the <monospace>Class</monospace> argument. In the code below, the TFR is calculated for each wealth quintile.</p>
      <list list-type="simple">
        <list-item>
          <p>
            <monospace>&gt; fert(ZWIR71,Indicator = "tfr", Class = "v190")</monospace>
          </p>
        </list-item>
        <list-item>
          <p>
            <monospace>The current function calculated TFR based on a reference period of 36 months</monospace>
          </p>
        </list-item>
        <list-item>
