      </list>
      <p>All the fertility rates above are calculated based on a reference period of 36 months (3 years) preceding the survey. The rates can also be calculated for different time periods; in the code below the TFR is calculated for 60 months (5 years) preceding the survey by declaring the <monospace>Period</monospace> argument, as below.</p>
      <list list-type="simple">
        <list-item>
          <p>
            <monospace>&gt; fert(ZWIR71,Indicator = "tfr", Period = 60)</monospace>
          </p>
        </list-item>
        <list-item>
          <p>
