        <p>Similarly, the <monospace>chmortp</monospace> function can be used to calculate the childhood component death probabilities, as below, where arguments like <monospace>Weight, Date_of_interview, Date_of_birth, Age_at_death, Class, Period</monospace> and <monospace>PeriodEnd</monospace> can be used in the same way as in the case of the <monospace>chmortp</monospace> function.</p>
